[perl #126482] <https://rt.perl.org/Public/Bug/Display.html?id=126482>
.IP "\(bu" 4
Many issues relating to \f(CW\*(C`printf "%a"\*(C'\fR of hexadecimal floating point
were fixed.  In addition, the \*(L"subnormals\*(R" (formerly known as \*(L"denormals\*(R")
