.IP "\(bu" 4
List assignment to \f(CW\*(C`vec\*(C'\fR or \f(CW\*(C`substr\*(C'\fR with an array or hash for its first
argument used to result in crashes or \*(L"Can't coerce\*(R" error messages at run
